snippet.title: YO-KAI WATCH 3 - The Tale of Two Yo-kai Watches Trailer - Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Nate Adams, a very average boy, and Hailey Anne Thomas, a budding detective, are two Yo-kai Watch owners in two very different places. Find out what mysteries they’ll solve in YO-KAI WATCH 3 on 2/8!
